{
  "stem": "21731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we went again on this diplomatic train, and it took a week, which was, even then, a very long time to go from Warsaw to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My grandfather died in Poland, in 1918.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my grandmother came back alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She had to-- there was an-- a younger sister of my mother, who lived with her parents in this flat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So grandmother was only with her younger daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She was 18 years younger than my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was quite a difference.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, I missed my grandfather very, very much, because he was good company for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He always had something for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He always had tales to tell me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was good company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mentioned before, the schools we went to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now I think I have to come to the end of my school days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did I mention that we went to the theater?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I mentioned it-- very-- very often.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother was also very strict with our readings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to learn-- to know English classics, like Dickens, Jules Verne, one or two books of Agatha Christie, I remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- she told us-- and we had to read the Polish classics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did not speak Polish, neither my brother nor I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think we were ashamed of speaking Polish, because none of our colleagues or our friends, spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we just refused to speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had an idea about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But mother introduced us to Mickiewicz and Sienkiewicz, and all those Polish writers, which we read in German, which was not the same as the book which I read later in the original language.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very different.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
